# Protect Main Branch

Before new work starts, make sure the checked-in ruleset is active on GitHub.

## Requirement

The `main` branch should have the `Protect main` ruleset applied:

- block branch deletion
- block force pushes
- require pull requests before merge
- require required status checks before merge

## Workflow

1. Run `./.github/scripts/sync_main_ruleset.sh`
2. Verify the repository includes the `Protect main` ruleset
3. Never push directly to `main`
